ngsteen@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jeremy-allen-white-bruce-springsteen@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jeremy-allen-white-bruce-springsteen@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jeremy-allen-white-bruce-springsteen@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jeremy-allen-white-bruce-springsteen@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-bear"><em>《熊》</em></a>明星杰里米·艾伦·怀特有望在一部即将上映的关于布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 1982 年专辑《内布拉斯加》制作的电影中饰演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/music-biopics-best-to-see-before-you-die-3401944">生前值得一看的 50 部音乐传记片</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/03/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white-movie-scott-stuber-nebraska-scott-cooper-directing-a24-ellen-goldsmith-vein-1235868961/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>好莱坞截止日期报道</em></a>，怀特是最有可能在这部影片中扮演年轻的斯普林斯汀的人选。据报道，该片名为<em>《从无处拯救我</em>》，该片将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-reportedly-working-on-film-of-the-making-of-nebraska-3570491">今年一月上映</a>。 <em>Deadline</em>指出，与 White 的谈判尚未开始，受欢迎的电影公司 A24 正在就加入该项目进行谈判。 </p><figure id="attachment_3567316" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3567316" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3567316" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="杰里米·艾伦·怀特" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3567316" class="wp-caption-text">杰里米·艾伦·怀特（Jeremy Allen White）——图片来源：Michael Tran /法新社，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>斯科特·库珀（Scott Cooper）曾执导过杰夫·布里吉斯（Jeff Bridges）领衔的<em>《疯狂的心</em>》、 <em>《黑色弥撒》</em> 、 <em>《鹿角</em>》等影片，他将执导这部即将上映的电影。据<em>报道</em>，斯普林斯汀和他的经理乔恩·兰道也积极参与了该项目，但目前尚不清楚更多细节。</p><p> <em>《Deliver Me From Nowhere》</em>将记录斯普林斯汀制作备受喜爱的《内布拉斯加》唱片的过程，该唱片在斯普林斯汀和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band">E Street Band</a>录制《诞生于美国》时开始成形。这部电影也是根据沃伦·赞斯的书<i>《从无处拯救我：布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀的内布拉斯加的制作》改编的</i>。</p><p> 《内布拉斯加》是斯普林斯汀的第六张专辑，由于录音的精简性质，它在他的目录中脱颖而出。当时他正经历一段黑暗的心理时期，用四轨录音机录制了一批歌曲作为小样，打算与E街乐队重新录制。最终，这位歌手决定按原样发布演示版。 </p><figure id="attachment_3596741" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3596741" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3596741" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/BruceSpringsteen-Best-Of-greatest-hits-news.jpg" alt="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/BruceSpringsteen-Best-Of-greatest-hits-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/BruceSpringsteen-Best-Of-greatest-hits-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/BruceSpringsteen-Best-Of-greatest-hits-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/BruceSpringsteen-Best-Of-greatest-hits-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/BruceSpringsteen-Best-Of-greatest-hits-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/BruceSpringsteen-Best-Of-greatest-hits-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3596741" class="wp-caption-text">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀现场表演。图片来源：迈克·科波拉/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>在布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀的其他新闻中，Boss 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-mark-knopfler-star-studded-going-home-teenage-cancer-trust-3601691">参加了马克·诺夫勒 (Mark Knopfler) 众星云集的慈善节目《回家》(Going Home) 的重新录制</a>，该节目的主演包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">皇后</a>乐队 (Queen) 的布莱恩·梅 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">Brian May)</a> 、布鲁斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen)</a> 、黑色安息日 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a> ) 的托尼·伊奥米 (Tony Iommi)、埃里克·克莱普顿 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">Eric Clapton)</a>等。 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德</a>等等。</p><p>他还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-cameo-curb-your-enthusiasm-larry-david-3586431">最近一集中客串了<i>《遏制你的热情》</i></a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-announces-new-greatest-hits-album-3596733">宣布了其职业生涯合辑的详细信息，题为《布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀精选》</a> ，将于 4 月 19 日星期五通过索尼音乐发行。</p><p>今年夏天晚些时候，The Boss 将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-announces-2024-uk-and-european-tour-buy-tickets-3526665">2024 年英国和爱尔兰巡演</a>回到池塘的这一边 - <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-tickets%2Fartist%2F860453" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到所有剩余的门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-bear-star-jeremy-allen-white-favourite-bruce-springsteen-nebraska-film-3609892">《熊》主演杰里米·艾伦·怀特有望在电影《内布拉斯加》中扮演布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀，该片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
