7/splendour-in-the-grass-2022-festival-review.jpg" alt="2022年草地辉煌音乐节回顾" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/splendour-in-the-grass-2022-festival-review.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/splendour-in-the-grass-2022-festival-review-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/splendour-in-the-grass-2022-festival-review-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/splendour-in-the-grass-2022-festival-review-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/splendour-in-the-grass-2022-festival-review-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/splendour-in-the-grass-2022-festival-review-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3276428" class="wp-caption-text"> 2022 年 Splendor In The Grass 的投注者。图片来源：Matt Jelonek/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>如果音乐节被取消，这将是继 Groovin The Moo 音乐节之后，澳大利亚今年第二个被取消的大型音乐节，后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/groovin-the-moo-2024-cancelled-ticket-refunds-3587121">因门票销量低而宣布取消</a>。该巡演音乐节原定于今年四月举行，艾莉森仙境 (Alison Wonderland)、Mura Masa、Wu-Tang Clan&#39;s GZA、DMA&#39;S、King Stingray 和 The Kooks 等都将出现在演出名单上。</p><p>据报道，Groovin The Moo&#39;s 和 Splendor In The Grass 的取消将导致近年来一系列音乐节被取消， <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/falls-festival-australia-2023-24-cancelled-3444530">去年瀑布音乐节宣布不会在 2023/2024 音乐节回归，以便让组织者有机会“休息、恢复和恢复”。重新校准”</a> 。</p><p>本月早些时候， <em>NME</em>的尼克·巴克利 (Nick Buckley)<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/australia-music-festival-closures-3603106">与主办方和行业领袖讨论了澳大利亚音乐节在疫情后面临的困境</a>，以及需要采取哪些措施来确保他们的未来。</p><p>该行业的顶级机构澳大利亚节日协会常务董事米奇·威尔逊 (Mitch Wilson) 告诉<em>《NME》</em> ，多年来的复杂挑战已使该行业陷入悬崖：COVID-19 大流行封锁、不可预测的天气事件、消费者信心以及下一代年轻人的兴趣减弱节日游行队伍。</p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/australias-splendour-in-the-grass-has-reportedly-been-cancelled-3609906">，澳大利亚的《Splendor In The Grass》已被取消的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href=